presentationColumns.name: 144  Trailing N Mth Rev  (Alias Based)
presentationColumns.description:
Help :
Revenue data. Sources from Revenue physical column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Billed time. 

- Rolling 3 months sum as of selected month : sum of current month plus previous two months value. For January, it gives the value of January plus December and November of the previous year
presentationColumns.sourceLogicalColumn: logicalColumn:Sample App.Time Series and Level Based Examples.144  Trailing N Mth Rev  (Alias Based)

presentationColumns.name: 145  Trailing N Mth Rev Daily Avg
presentationColumns.description:
Help :
Revenue data. Sources from Revenue physical column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Billed time. 

- Daily average over Rolling 3 months period : Rolling 3 months sum as of selected month divided by number of days in R3M period.
